text: Dominican University (DU) is a private Catholic university in River Forest, Illinois. It has a bachelor's and master's degrees and certificate programs. Dominican University offers more than 50 majors in the Rosary College of Arts and Sciences and 20 programs in five graduate academic divisions. ==References== Category:1900s establishments in Illinois Category:1901 establishments in the United States Category:Colleges and universities in Illinois Category:Christian colleges and universities in the United States Category:Cook County, Illinois
